{"tid":1637860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"安信兄弟原來係中旅社嫁","createTime":"2019-10-08T06:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T07:02:58.000Z","uid":19592,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0a1453c40554947a3af5949f017085a63fa0f83","tid":1637860,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"如題 安信兄弟好似都唔少街鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c64634b3938edc2237ec476c2cf3ac8da9540b7","tid":1637860,"uid":88982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"嘩 原來老共做埋放數架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a36eecc91612f255b694515ed74e3ed359e24a7","tid":1637860,"uid":43493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"渣打銀行附屬機構嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f979ac7ded68430512fff8aa779d7729888cbd","tid":1637860,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkctfh.com/aboutself/introduction/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctfh.com%2Faboutself%2Fintroduction%2Findex.html&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=ab0e1ad9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkctfh.com/aboutself/introduction/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n消費金融業務是中旅金控的另一引擎業務。中旅金控牽頭並購原渣打銀行旗下的香港安信信貸有限公司，聯合的另外兩方股東分别是澳大利亞領先的非銀行消費信貸機構Pepper集團以及采用多元化投資策略的國際投資機構York資本。安信信貸成立於1977年，已有40年歷史，目前是香港最大的非銀行消費信貸公司，發展穩健。安信信貸中國業務以深圳爲基礎，全速擴張；公司於2016年底獲得全國性互聯網貸款業務牌照，並於2017年初獲準開業，将在突出特色、防控風險的基礎上，逐步拓展至全國市場。"},{"pid":"52f3b703e2687ce196554272703729d9c94e4c60","tid":1637860,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a36eecc91612f255b694515ed74e3ed359e24a7","tid":1637860,"uid":43493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"渣打銀行附屬機構嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:00:06.000Z","msg":"一早賣撚左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3a38ed136e5975ad41ffcca937acda0d47ff90","tid":1637860,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c64634b3938edc2237ec476c2cf3ac8da9540b7","tid":1637860,"uid":88982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"嘩 原來老共做埋放數架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:02:58.000Z","msg":"其實好多中資都成為左好多行業既龍頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}